title: Bad Ideas -- Ethan Deiss #LIVEARNETTE
description: Ethan Deiss is lucky to be alive, having nearly escaped being killed in a sketchy hotel. In this #LIVEARNETTE episode, Ethan tells you his scary experiences while filming for his first videopart, Bad Ideas.
